resources.string:
Skapa en Intent:
 Intent i = new Intent(this,ActivityToStart.class);

 Starta Activity:
 startActivity(i);

Skapa en Intent:
 Intent i = new Intent(this,ActivityToStart.class);

 Infoga data:
 i.putExtra("Age", 23);
 i.putExtra("Name", "Eva");

Hämta referens till Intent:
 Intent i = getIntent();

 Avläsa data:
 int age = i.getIntExtra("Age");
 String name = i.getStringExtra("Name");
